						<p  style="text-align: justify; margin-right: 120px;" style="margin-bottom: 1px;">
							<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">&quot;Shall I tell you the joys of the Jetta station wagon, dude? It&#39;s low-profile. It&#39;s got it all. The instrumentation, while firmly rooted in the twenty-first century, could easily be mistaken for 1993. The steering wheel has nothing but the steering wheel ... The funny thing is, Susan&#39;s and my lifestyle -- as much as it&#39;s about home and creating something warm -- it&#39;s still an image thing no matter how you slice it, the same way it&#39;s as much of an ego trip to drive the Jetta as it is the Bentley. One&#39;s a judgment on the other, and one&#39;s a counterjudgment, and God bless the Prius, but that ain&#39;t me.&quot;</span></p>
